## **üîß PHASE 2: TECHNISCHE INFRASTRUKTUR**

### **2.1 NFC-Redirect-System**

**Flow:**
```
1. User scannt Chip
2. URL: nfc.severmore.de/t/{UID}?sun={CMAC}
3. Backend:
   - Verifiziert SUN (NTAG424 DNA Security)
   - Sucht Chip UID in DB
   - Ermittelt aktiven "Mode"
   - Redirect zu Target URL
```

**DB Schema (Supabase):**
```sql
-- Chips Table
chips (
  id: uuid (PK)
  uid: string (Unique, NFC Chip UID)
  company_id: uuid (FK -> companies)
  assigned_user_id: uuid (FK -> users, nullable)
  active_mode: enum (corporate, hospitality, campaign)
  created_at: timestamp
  last_scan: timestamp
)

-- Companies Table
companies (
  id: uuid (PK)
  name: string
  plan: enum (starter, pro, enterprise)
  crm_integration: jsonb (Salesforce/HubSpot Config)
  created_at: timestamp
)

-- Users Table (Mitarbeiter)
users (
  id: uuid (PK)
  company_id: uuid (FK)
  email: string
  name: string
  job_title: string
  profile_pic: string (URL)
  vcard_data: jsonb (Kontaktdaten)
  social_links: jsonb (LinkedIn, etc.)
  ghost_mode: boolean (404 bei Scan)
  created_at: timestamp
)

-- Scans Table (Analytics)
scans (
  id: uuid (PK)
  chip_id: uuid (FK)
  user_id: uuid (FK, nullable)
  scan_time: timestamp
  ip_address: string
  user_agent: string
  location: jsonb (optional: Geo-Data)
  mode_at_scan: enum
)

-- Leads Table
leads (
  id: uuid (PK)
  chip_id: uuid (FK)
  captured_by_user_id: uuid (FK)
  lead_name: string
  lead_email: string
  lead_phone: string (optional)
  sentiment: enum (hot, warm, cold) -- Ampel
  notes: text
  created_at: timestamp
  follow_up_sent: boolean
)

-- Campaign Overrides
campaign_overrides (
  id: uuid (PK)
  company_id: uuid (FK)
  target_url: string
  active: boolean
  start_date: timestamp
  end_date: timestamp
)
```

***

### **2.2 Dynamic Routing Engine**

**Backend Logic (Supabase Edge Functions):**

```javascript
// nfc-redirect.ts
export async function handler(req) {
  const { uid, sun } = req.query;
  
  // 1. Verify NTAG424 SUN
  if (!verifySUN(uid, sun)) {
    return redirect('/error/invalid-chip');
  }
  
  // 2. Lookup Chip in DB
  const chip = await supabase
    .from('chips')
    .select('*, company_id, assigned_user_id, active_mode')
    .eq('uid', uid)
    .single();
  
  if (!chip) return redirect('/error/chip-not-found');
  
  // 3. Log Scan
  await logScan(chip.id, req);
  
  // 4. Check Campaign Override
  const override = await getActiveOverride(chip.company_id);
  if (override) return redirect(override.target_url);
  
  // 5. Route by Mode
  switch (chip.active_mode) {
    case 'corporate':
      return redirect(`/profile/${chip.assigned_user_id}`);
    case 'hospitality':
      return redirect(`/review/${chip.company_id}`);
    case 'campaign':
      return redirect(`/campaign/${chip.company_id}`);
    default:
      return redirect('/error/mode-not-set');
  }
}
```

